Glucagon-like peptide-1 receptor regulation of basal dopamine transporter
activity is species-dependent
Mathias E. Jensena,∗, Aurelio Gallij, Morgane Thomsena, Kathrine L. Jensenb, Gerda K. Thomsenc,
Mette K. Klausena, Tina Vilsbølld,e, Mikkel B. Christensend,f, Jens J. Holstg, Anthony Owensh,
Sabrina Robertsoni, Lynette Dawsh, Daniele Zanellaj, Ulrik Getherb, Gitte M. Knudsenc,d,
Anders Fink-Jensena,d
